# 🍴 PyFood – Food Ordering System (Python)

PyFood is a console-based food ordering system built using **Object-Oriented Programming in Python**.  
It demonstrates user management, restaurant menus, cart functionality, and order processing — all organized in a modular architecture.

---

## 🚀 Features
- User registration and login system  
- Add, view, and manage food items  
- Interactive menu system using classes and inheritance  
- Cart operations (add, remove, checkout)  
- Modular folder structure for scalability  

